What is this?

7
00:00:14,372 --> 00:00:16,200
這是你的
This is yours.

8
00:00:16,235 --> 00:00:18,167
也是我的
And mine.

9
00:00:18,202 --> 00:00:20,938
有位幸運的先生把傳説中的蘇糖買走了
Some lucky gent has taken the legendary Sugar off the market.

10
00:00:20,973 --> 00:00:23,194
我們還沒享受到她的魅力呢
Before we'd had the benefit of her charms.

11
00:00:23,229 --> 00:00:26,280
恐怕得説一切並不理想 你的子宮已經移位
I'm afraid all is not as it should be. Your womb has moved.

12
00:00:26,315 --> 00:00:28,765
艾格尼絲流産過?
Agnes lost a child?

13
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:32,308
不 孩子生下來了      你們有小孩?
No, we have a child. We have?

14
00:00:32,343 --> 00:00:33,445
是個女孩 索菲
A daughter. Sophie.

15
00:00:33,480 --> 00:00:36,704
不舒服時 我就吃上兩片
On bad days I take a couple of these.

16
00:00:37,332 --> 00:00:42,845
相信我 你會連自己都不認得的
Trust me, you will hardly know yourself.

17
00:00:42,880 --> 00:00:46,400
我有個守護天使      我會回來找你的
I have a guardian angel. I will come back for you.

18
00:00:46,435 --> 00:00:49,920
我多麼渴望能和你住在一起
I wish for all the world that I could live with you.

19
00:00:49,955 --> 00:00:51,720
你們家族的男人腦子都有問題嗎?
What is the matter with the men in your family?

20
00:00:51,755 --> 00:00:55,602
福克斯太太快死了
Mrs Fox is dying.

21
00:00:55,637 --> 00:00:56,760
等不及想讓你也來了
I can't wait for you to join me.

22
00:00:57,260 --> 00:00:59,385
我不能作爲家庭教師
Could I not, in fact,

23
00:00:59,420 --> 00:01:01,860
和你住在一起嗎?
live with you as your new governess?

24
