37
00:02:30,740 --> 00:02:34,025
我們的見面能讓你放鬆嗎?
restorative you find our time together?

38
00:02:34,060 --> 00:02:40,900
沒錯 因此我想讓你搬到切普斯托路去
Indeed. Which is why I would like you to move to Chepstow Villas.

39
00:02:40,935 --> 00:02:42,540
做索菲的家庭教師
And become Sophie's governess.

40
00:02:45,220 --> 00:02:46,980
登堂入室
To live in your house?

41
00:02:49,100 --> 00:02:53,545
和你住在一起?      你不是也想這樣嗎?
With you? I thought that was what you wanted?

42
